},
{
"text": "These forms are transported to factories to be manufactured into products such as foil, cans, and car parts.",
"source": "health_book_draft:chapter_three_section_1"
}
]
},
{
"type": "rule",
"canonical_name": "Energy intensity of aluminum production",
